This Terraform configuration sets up an AWS RDS Aurora MySQL cluster with enhanced connection management through instance proxies. It includes a VPC, RDS IAM role, security group, subnets, and a secret stored in AWS Secrets Manager for secure credential management. Adjust the instance classes and subnet IDs based on your needs and AWS environment.

